《'''亞美尼亞大地震'''》（{{lang-hy|երկրաշարժ}}，{{lang-ru|Землетрясение}}）是一部2016年的[[亞美尼亞|亞美尼亞]][[災難片|災難]][[劇情片|劇情片]]，為[[薩里克·安卓斯楊|薩里克·安卓斯楊]]執導和監製，改編自1988年的真實事件[[亞美尼亞大地震|亞美尼亞大地震]]<ref name="Panorama">{{cite web |url=http://www.panorama.am/en/news/2016/07/11/%E2%80%9CEarthquake%E2%80%9D-in-Gyumri/1610309 |title=Screening of Sarik Andreasyan’s "Earthquake" in Gyumri |work=Panorama |date=2016-09-03 |accessdate=2016-09-03 |archive-date=2019-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191013202954/https://www.panorama.am/en/news/2016/07/11/%E2%80%9CEarthquake%E2%80%9D-in-Gyumri/1610309 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="asbarez">{{cite web |url=http://asbarez.com/154564/armenian-national-film-academy-receives-3-applications-for-oscars-submission/ |title=Armenian National Film Academy Receives 3 Applications for Oscars Submission |work=Asbarez |date=2016-09-03 |accessdate=2016-09-03 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022231645/http://asbarez.com/154564/armenian-national-film-academy-receives-3-applications-for-oscars-submission/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影在亞美尼亞於2016年9月13日上映。

該片被選入[[第89屆奧斯卡金像獎|第89屆奧斯卡金像獎]]的[[奧斯卡最佳外語片獎|最佳外語片]]代表亞美尼亞的候選片<ref name="Armenia">{{cite web |url=http://www.panarmenian.net/eng/news/220009/ |title=Armenia picks "Earthquake" for foreign language Oscar race |work=Panarmenian |date=2016-09-03 |accessdate=2016-09-03 |archive-date=2016-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160904161355/http://www.panarmenian.net/eng/news/220009/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="HWR">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-armenia-selects-earthquake-foreign-925678 |title=Oscars: Armenia Selects 'Earthquake' for Foreign-Language Category |last=Holdsworth |first=Nick |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2016-09-04 |accessdate=2016-09-05 |archive-date=2016-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103222400/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-armenia-selects-earthquake-foreign-925678 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但因電影不符合提交要求而被學院取消資格<ref name="Disqualified">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/foreign-language-oscar-armenian-submission-937903 |title=Foreign-Language Oscar: Armenian Submission Disqualified |last=Kozlov |first=Vladimir |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2016-10-12 |accessdate=2016-10-13 |archive-date=2016-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103222541/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/foreign-language-oscar-armenian-submission-937903 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="DQ">{{cite web |url=http://www.panarmenian.net/eng/news/223075/ |title=Armenia’s Oscar entry creators explain Academy’s disqualification |work=Panarmenian |date=2016-10-13 |accessdate=2016-10-13 |archive-date=2019-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190722174711/http://www.panarmenian.net/eng/news/223075/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 劇情 ==
1988年12月7日，在亞美尼亞發生了一場史無前例的大地震，而造成嚴重的傷亡，這使得劫後餘生的人們必須相互幫助，以尋找四散的家人並度過這漫長的黑暗時刻。

